{"tid":1859734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[小心］上星期五係旺角呢間舖到買左d有問題口罩","createTime":"2020-02-03T10:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T07:56:26.000Z","uid":125091,"like":470,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c0ac3062f1f1898861806aaee8d95fff2d9fff","tid":1859734,"uid":125091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T10:19:19.000Z","msg":"因為擔心屋企人就黎冇口罩用，所以情急之下就去左下邊呢間工程用品舖，打算買d口罩俾家母應急。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GkLup8v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGkLup8v.png&h=56eeff8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買左呢款口罩：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/koqFwPb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkoqFwPb.jpg&h=cac36911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知一開黎用發現d口罩異常地啡左一噠同有陣怪味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vLY4d3u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvLY4d3u.jpg&h=7245fb91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iH69qaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiH69qaa.jpg&h=765abb6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n盒口罩成$300/20個，我盛怒之下就去翻間舖到同老闆理論，但一聽到我話d貨有事，就話我係咪搞事同話報警，我拍拍佢心口答：「報警？依家邊有警察理你呀？」<br />\n<br />\n最後重想就咁拎翻盒口罩扮冇野，成個過程個老闆都冇打算道歉，就咁話佢地都係買翻黎佢地都唔知，我唔俾佢拎到盒口罩先肯退翻$300蚊了事，d職員重要加句：「不過你依家冇口罩用了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢到奉勸各位最好唔好係呢間野到買口罩，一黎d貨可能有問題，佢地唔覺得關自己事，二黎呢間野係為左收錢出貨完全冇乜道德可言</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n祝大家身體健康"},{"pid":"dcb96b61f7dbbec628967e175ba9d00ca96779af","tid":1859734,"uid":125091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T10:19:59.000Z","msg":"自推x1"},{"pid":"9c5c490b4b8fe659a4adc706501b0551bbac3446","tid":1859734,"uid":125091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T10:20:09.000Z","msg":"自推x2"},{"pid":"5178697640b7dac94b10d2576aa2968623d6460e","tid":1859734,"uid":343361,"l