口罩異常地啡左一噠同有陣怪味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vLY4d3u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvLY4d3u.jpg&h=7245fb91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iH69qaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiH69qaa.jpg&h=765abb6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n盒口罩成$300/20個，我盛怒之下就去翻間舖到同老闆理論，但一聽到我話d貨有事，就話我係咪搞事同話報警，我拍拍佢心口答：「報警？依家邊有警察理你呀？」<br />\n<br />\n最後重想就咁拎翻盒口罩扮冇野，成個過程個老闆都冇打算道歉，就咁話佢地都係買翻黎佢地都唔知，我唔俾佢拎到盒口罩先肯退翻$300蚊了事，d職員重要加句：「不過你依家冇口罩用了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢到奉勸各位最好唔好係呢間野到買口罩，一黎d貨可能有問題，佢地唔覺得關自己事，二黎呢間野係為左收錢出貨完全冇乜道德可言</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n祝大家身體健康"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:32:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3aa3f6f077671be2c1be305c0df462db8cc0158","tid":1859734,"uid":226216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:33:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe2ce11eda8380934e8b1a68a6f7cad1bfe8f9b8","tid":1859734,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:33:57.000Z","msg":"支持攬炒"},{"pid":"5658616bc0a66eabaffe7ae22aa713d0c174ed10","tid":1859734,"uid":144541,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"89741f29bbddd385ee3d942c4852229603bb42c9","tid":1859734,"uid":125091,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"89430a3d70138b8dab9baaba24afdec153121fbe","tid":1859734,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc7c4886462b8449efe7aecd0653ac31407e5b4a","tid":1859734,"uid":125091,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T10:24:59.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢上黎連提大家重要d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T10:29:53.000Z","msg":"你溝條女返黎，要比連仔屌完，你先上？<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，死廢柴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T10:31:55.000Z","msg":"我唔想浪費時間係呢個體制上面，我上黎講只係想幫人<br />\n<br />\nBtw 屌你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T11:34:57.000Z","msg":"你想幫人就報海關啦<img